                <h2 class="heading" data-aos="fade">History</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="timeline-item" date-is='2019' data-aos="fade">
                    <h3>A Symbol of Malaysian Hospitality</h3>
                    <p style="text-align: justify;">Over the decades, the hotel has become a proud ambassador of Malaysian hospitality. Hosting international events and welcoming guests from all over the world, it reflects the nation’s diversity and warmth. Today, the hotel continues to evolve, incorporating sustainable practices and modern amenities while preserving the rich traditions that make Malaysia a unique destination.</p>
                    
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item" date-is='2011' data-aos="fade">
                    <h3>Expanding Across the Peninsula</h3>
                    <p style="text-align: justify;">
                        Following the success of its flagship property, the hotel expanded its footprint across Malaysia, opening branches in Penang, Johor Bahru, and Kota Kinabalu. Each location was carefully chosen to showcase the natural beauty and cultural heritage of the region. From the serene beaches of Langkawi to the lively streets of George Town, the hotel became synonymous with luxury and local charm.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item" date-is='2008' data-aos="fade">
                    <h3>The Beginnings in Kuala Lumpur</h3>
                    <p style="text-align: justify;">
                        Nestled in the heart of Kuala Lumpur, the hotel’s journey began in the early 1980s with a vision to provide a unique blend of modern comfort and Malaysian warmth. Strategically located near the bustling streets of Bukit Bintang, the first branch quickly became a favorite among business travelers and tourists alike. The hotel’s commitment to authentic hospitality, coupled with Malaysia’s vibrant culture, set the stage for a legacy of excellence.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>
